#: ../../pyvista/doc/source/examples/99-advanced/plotting_algorithms.rst:32
msgid ""
"A :vtk:`vtkAlgorithm` is the superclass for all sources, filters, and sinks "
"in VTK. It defines a generalized interface for executing data processing "
"algorithms. Pipeline connections are associated with input and output ports "
"that are independent of the type of data passing through the connections."
